'''Sheikh Hamdan Bin Zayed Stadium''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Madinat Zayed]], [[United Arab Emirates]].  It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home ground of [[Dhafra]]. It holds 5,020 people.
