'''City Yangon Football Club''' is a Myanmar [[association football|football]] club,founded in 2012. Originating from Horizon International Schools, the team switched to full Professional Club status and contested the MNL-2. At the end of [[2016 Myanmar National League]], they relegated to [[MNL-2]]. At the end of the 2016 MNL season, [[Horizon F.C.|Horizon]] name changed to '''City Yangon'''.
The team has been dethroned after competition of 2017 MNL-2 season due to financial difficulty as the team chairman has been added as "Blacklist".

