{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2013}} {{Infobox venue | stadium_name = Ecolog Arena | nickname = '''Ecolog Arena''' | image = StadiumTetovo.jpg | caption = | fullname = Ecolog Arena | former_names = The stadium of the city of Tetovo/Stadioni i qytetit | location = [[Tetovo]], Macedonia | coordinates = {{Coord|42.0186|20.9783|region:MK_type:landmark|format=dms|display=inline,title}} | built = 1980 | opened = {{Start date|1981|07|26|df=y}} | renovated = 2017 | owner = [[KF Shkëndija|Shkëndija]] | operator = [[KF Shkëndija|Shkëndija]] | surface = [[Grass]] | scoreboard = [[LED display|LED]] | estimated_cost = | suites = | architect = | project_manager = | structural engineer = | services engineer = | general_contractor = | main_contractors = | capacity = 15,000<ref>http://stadiumdb.com/stadiums/mkd/stadion_gradski_tetovo</ref> | record_attendance = | dimensions = | tenants = [[KF Shkëndija|Shkëndija]] }}
'''Ecolog Arena''' (formerly known as '''City Stadium Tetovo''') is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Tetovo]], [[Republic of Macedonia]]. It is currently used for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches. The stadium holds 15,000.<ref>http://www.worldfootballtravel.com/stadium/europe/macedonia/city-stadium-tetovo/</ref>
In March 2015, has been signed agreement between [[Football Federation of Macedonia]] and [[Tetovo Municipality]] for the renovation of stadium as a part of project of [[UEFA]], „Hat-trick 4".<ref>{{cite web |url=http://sportmedia.mk/potpishan-dogovorot-za-rekonstruktsija-tetovo-ke-dobie-moderen-stadion-za-nokni-mechevi/ |title=Потпишан договорот за реконструкција: Тетово ќе добие модерен стадион за ноќни мечеви |publisher=Sportmedia.mk |date=10 March 2015 |accessdate=15 March 2015 |language=Macedonian |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150320021605/http://sportmedia.mk/potpishan-dogovorot-za-rekonstruktsija-tetovo-ke-dobie-moderen-stadion-za-nokni-mechevi/ |archivedate=20 March 2015 |df=dmy-all }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://ekipa.mk/potpishan-dogovorot-za-rekonstruktsija-na-gradskiot-stadion-vo-tetovo/ |title=Потпишан договорот за реконструкција на Градскиот стадион во Тетово|publisher=Ekipa.mk |date=10 March 2015 |accessdate=15 March 2015|language=Macedonian}}</ref> The renovation of stadium began in April 2015.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ekipa.mk/startuvashe-rekonstruktsijata-i-na-stadionot-vo-tetovo-foto/ |title=Стартуваше реконструкцијата и на стадионот во Тетово (ФОТО)|publisher=Ekipa.mk |date=16 April 2015 |accessdate=18 April 2015|language=Macedonian}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://sport365.mk/po-bitola-i-vo-tetovo-zapocnaa-gradeznite-raboti-na-stadionot/ |title=По Битола, и во Тетово започнаа градежните работи на стадионот |publisher=Sport365.mk |date=16 April 2015 |accessdate=18 April 2015 |language=Macedonian |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304090330/http://sport365.mk/po-bitola-i-vo-tetovo-zapocnaa-gradeznite-raboti-na-stadionot/ |archivedate=4 March 2016 |df=dmy-all }}</ref> In April 2016, the renovation works on the pitch were finished,<ref>{{cite web |url=http://sportmedia.com.mk/fudbal/domashno-prvenstvo/po-edna-godina-tetovskite-ekipi-se-vrakjaat-na-svojot-stadion |title=Шкендија и Ренова први ќе го сефтосаат новиот стадион во Тетово! |publisher=Sportmedia.mk |date=4 April 2016 |accessdate=5 April 2016|language=Macedonian}}</ref> and later that year floodlights for playing matches at night were added.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ekipa.mk/postaveni-reflektori-na-gradskiot-stadion-vo-tetovo/ |title=Поставени рефлектори на Градскиот стадион во Тетово |publisher=Ekipa.mk |date=10 July 2016 |accessdate=11 July 2016|language=Macedonian}}</ref>
In July 2016, Ecolog International, the owners of KF Shkëndija, took the Tetovo City Stadium under concession from the municipal council, as well as a second ground committing to invest 7.7 million euros in order to make stadium meet the criteria for international matches.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.shqipmedia.com/eksluzive-ecolog-merr-oficialisht-stadiumin-e-tetoves/ |title=Eksluzive: Ecolog merr oficialisht stadiumin e Tetovës |publisher=shqipmedia.com |date=19 July 2016 |accessdate=29 July 2016|language=Albanian}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.yllpress.com/135198/miratohet-vendimi-per-dhenie-me-koncesion-te-dy-stadiumeve-futbollistike-te-tetoves.html |title=Miratohet Vendimi për dhënie me koncesion të dy stadiumeve futbollistike të Tetovës |publisher=yllpress.com |date=19 July 2016 |accessdate=29 July 2016|language=Albanian}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://lajmi.net/destani-merr-dy-stadiumet-e-tetoves-ku-pritet-te-investoje-8-milione-euro/ |title=Destani merr dy stadiumet e Tetovës ku pritet të investojë 8 milionë euro |publisher=lajmi.net |date=19 July 2016 |accessdate=29 July 2016|language=Albanian}}</ref> The ground has been renamed Ecolog Arena.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://fax.al/read/news/4714527/12255802/ecolog-arena-bekim-tateshi-edhe-kesaj-rradhe-u-vertetua-se-jemi-popull-privat |title="ECOLOG ARENA", Bekim Tateshi: Edhe kësaj rradhe u vërtetua se jemi popull privat |work=fax.al |date=19 July 2016 |accessdate=2 August 2016|language=Albanian}}</ref>
